3/The big one for March though is Garden Day aka Spring Equinox - Generally around March 21st. Do some gardening, get outside, feel the soil under your bare feet. Review your goals and aspirations for the year. Meditate on happiness. Gather with friends.

2/ March 14th is world Pi Day. On this day we celebrate math and eat pie. Sharing pie with math lovers is a very Bald Jesus thing to do. If you are baking pies, cut the pi symbol in the top of your pie!

of course, all these prices are going to be cancelled in a couple of days when OS resets and my thought is to set the floor of all the BJs I still have at something like .05 ETH. So, what does that mean?

At some point ‚Äì Bald Jesus is going to get the attention of an influencer or a media story because we are not going to disappear. I‚Äôve got all the original OG Bald Jesus NFTs listed for these kind of giveaway prices ‚Äì
